07:25.144 --> 07:27.135
Maybe I'll tell you in Italy.

07:29.982 --> 07:33.850
Do you think it means something
that we're both left-handed?

07:33.920 --> 07:38.323
We'd only need one pair of scissors
if we moved in together.

07:38.391 --> 07:43.488
