their construction back a few months

09:37.109 --> 09:38.371
while we excavate.

09:38.444 --> 09:39.741
Oh, and Beth?

09:39.812 --> 09:44.306
This could be something
worth presenting in Florence.

09:44.383 --> 09:46.283
What the fuck
do you want me to do, Robert?

09:46.352 --> 09:48.877
- I am here...
- I got to hop, this guy's killing me.

09:48.955 --> 09:50.217
God, I love the mute button.

09:50.289 --> 09:52.814
