Give him to me.

10:22.788 --> 10:24.813
Page five.

10:27.293 --> 10:29.022
You know you guys
are still cut off, right?

10:29.095 --> 10:30.653
Hey. This is actually Tom Fielding.

10:30.730 --> 10:32.061
I run the sales desk over here.

10:32.131 --> 10:33.962
How you doing, Tom?
John Caldwell.

10:34.033 --> 10:36.297
I was calling to ask
a yes or no question, all right?

10:36.369 --> 10:37.358
Fine.

10:37.436 --> 10:39.063
Are you potentially interested

10:39.138 --> 10:41.504
in trading Microsoft today, yes or no?

10:43.142 --> 10:45.770
Potentially.
But not with you guys.

10:45.845 --> 10:47.335
Bobby, this is going to happen.

10:47.413 --> 10:48.971
Now, just FYI,

10:49.048 --> 10:50.913
I have a guy looking
for a pretty big chunk.

10:50.983 --> 10:52.211
Maybe half a mile.

10:52.284 --> 10:56.050
- Does that interest you?
- Potentially. Sure.

10:56.122 --> 10:59.353
Unfortunately, John, I don't have
the luxury of a lot of time here.

10:59.458 --> 11:01.892
My guy's real.
He's on the phone for one call.

11:01.927 --> 11:03.519
