12:01.120 --> 12:02.417
Okay, fine.

12:02.488 --> 12:04.080
Put it up.
But, oh, Tom?

12:04.156 --> 12:06.181
You'll still be in the box
for a week, though.

12:07.426 --> 12:09.451
Cross at five million, clean.

12:09.528 --> 12:11.519
See how far a little trust can get you?

12:13.866 --> 12:15.834
