- Sounds like it.

18:26.772 --> 18:29.297
You got to see her.
She's so fucking hot.

18:29.374 --> 18:31.968
You should invite her to your place
for the mid-year dinner.

18:32.044 --> 18:34.012
Yeah. She can sit
right next to my wife.

18:34.079 --> 18:36.104
Can you imagine?

18:36.181 --> 18:37.739
