I'm sorry, baby, but you know
it doesn't work that way.

01:22:19.701 --> 01:22:21.999
Look, I lost my wallet tonight.

01:22:22.070 --> 01:22:23.469
And I will make it up to you.

01:22:23.538 --> 01:22:25.665
- I promise.
- Listen, motherfucker.

01:22:25.740 --> 01:22:27.970
You will get me
my motherfucking money

01:22:28.043 --> 01:22:29.738
or I'm going to fucking scream
until the fucking cops come.

01:22:29.811 --> 01:22:32.575
And that would fuck you a lot more
than it would fuck me.

01:22:32.647 --> 01:22:33.909
Okay, how about we just calm down.

01:22:33.982 --> 01:22:36.610
And I'll find a way to get
your money for you, okay?

01:22:36.685 --> 01:22:40.382
Just give me a minute
to think about it.

01:22:40.455 --> 01:22:43.390
Okay, baby.
Whenever you're ready.

01:22:48.263 --> 01:22:52.393
- Irv, how's it going?
- You can't go up there, son.

01:22:52.467 --> 01:22:54.662
I just need to talk
to Christie for a second.

01:22:54.736 --> 01:22:56.670
You're no longer on the guest list.

01:22:59.474 --> 01:23:01.601
Irv, look, my man,
I'm up there all the time.

01:23:01.676 --> 01:23:04.440
Donny, show this man to the door.

01:24:07.409 --> 01:24:09.343
I feel sorry for you, Tommy.

01:24:11.079 --> 01:24:12.137
I do.

01:24:20.922 --> 01:24:22.082
Thanks, baby.

01:24:24.859 --> 01:24:26.156
Two stops, please.

01:24:37.005 --> 01:24:40.202
So, that's how we got here.

01:24:42.277 --> 01:24:43.505
It's not pretty.

01:24:43.578 --> 01:24:45.603
I know.

01:24:48.483 --> 01:24:51.452
I really don't have anything left
to say for myself.

01:24:54.355 --> 01:24:55.982
Maybe that's a start.

01:24:58.426 --> 01:25:00.121
So, what are you going to do now?

01:25:01.863 --> 01:25:03.057
I don't know.

01:25:04.332 --> 01:25:05.321
Chris Baker,

01:25:05.400 --> 01:25:07.595
he keeps asking me to join
him at his new place,

01:25:07.669 --> 01:25:12.732
but I'm just not sure that's
what I want to do right now.

01:25:16.044 --> 01:25:18.410
Have you ever been up
in a hot air balloon?

01:25:19.781 --> 01:25:20.805
What?

01:25:22.050 --> 01:25:24.382
Never mind.

01:25:53.882 --> 01:25:55.747
Tommy.

01:26:12.734 --> 01:26:14.224
<i>Buon giorno, carissima.</i>

01:26:21.075 --> 01:26:24.408
Why did you come back
in that restaurant for my number?

01:26:25.647 --> 01:26:27.046
I just couldn't be with that other girl

01:26:27.115 --> 01:26:28.742
when all I wanted was to talk to you.

01:26:40.828 --> 01:26:42.921
Whatever happened to her, anyway?

01:26:45.833 --> 01:26:47.266
Just wasn't right.

01:26:50.338 --> 01:26:52.966
When you flipped that coin,

01:26:53.041 --> 01:26:56.204
and I said I wanted to stay,

01:26:56.277 --> 01:26:58.438
I don't think I realized it then,

01:26:58.546 --> 01:27:02.482
but I was thinking
about you when I said it.

01:27:02.517 --> 01:27:03.916
I know.

01:27:06.888 --> 01:27:09.049
So, what was it?

01:27:09.123 --> 01:27:11.557
What was what?

01:27:11.626 --> 01:27:12.752
Heads or tails?

01:27:14.095 --> 01:27:15.653
Stay or leave?

01:27:22.370 --> 01:27:23.769
That's what I thought.

